<D>__{doc! get up here! tex is hit!}
<A>__{chris, looking out to his front, has no clue what's going on. except the fire is slacking. relayed shouts of 'medic! medic!' other shouts.}
<C>__{shouts}
<D>__{hold it up! hold it up!}
<A>__{the firing has ceased. a silence, punctuated by occasional shouts and fast moments, has enveloped once more the cemetery. doc crashes through the bush, kneels over tex, who continues to howl in deep pain.}
