<A>__{barnes and big harold come hustling up. doc finishes tourniquetting tex, cradles chris onto the earth, his flashlight probing the wound. tex in background continues to thrash and moan. chris waits, tensely for the verdict, his eyes big with fear on doc, who takes out his morphine.}
<C>__{junior}
