<C>__{barnes}
<D>__{shut up! shut up and take it! take the pain!}
<A>__{tex's eyes roll wildly, uncomprehending. doc and big harold looking at barnes, wondering. tex is suddenly silent, shocked. barnes stands, an icy glare, goes. junior scrambles over to tex's side. doc runs off. big harold cradles chris, his big black hands like a mother, reassuring him.}
